            "type": "text",
            "text": "Travelers are encouraged to explore responsibly, ensuring that Artvin’s pristine environments and vibrant communities continue to thrive. Whether a seasoned trekker or a curious explorer, the hiking trails of Artvin await to share their breathtaking beauty and heartfelt stories."
